=Episode 40=

3
00:00:58,918 --> 00:01:03,913
(Everything is about to end.
May the future be all about clear skies)

4
00:01:04,439 --> 00:01:05,560
To be honest with you,

5
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:09,359
I'm also scared in my heart.

6
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:13,560
I won't joke with my own life.

7
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,519
Look at this sunshine.

8
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,680
Look at these waves.

9
00:01:19,159 --> 00:01:20,640
If my girlfriend is by my side,

10
00:01:21,359 --> 00:01:22,760
I also want a stable life.

11
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:28,799
Look.

12
00:01:30,239 --> 00:01:31,680
This is the essay

13
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,840
Huang Zhixing's daughter recently posted

14
00:01:34,359 --> 00:01:35,519
on her social media account,

15
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,120
(Xi's World)
"My Dad".

16
00:01:38,397 --> 00:01:42,253
♪You can't tell what he's laughing at♪

17
00:01:43,159 --> 00:01:44,920
(Every time he sees me,)

18
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,879
(he always overreacts.)

19
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:49,439
(But the childish one is not me,)

20
00:01:49,439 --> 00:01:50,439
(but him.)

21
00:01:50,879 --> 00:01:52,519
(At first, I didn't understand.)

22
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:54,920
(But later, I felt)

23
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:57,640
(he seemed to be saying goodbye to me.)

24
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:59,719
(Every day he is saying goodbye.)

25
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,840
(One time, I asked him...)

26
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:06,280
Dad.

27
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:08,520
Will you suddenly disappear one day?

28
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,960
(I thought he would say,)

29
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:12,159
("I will always be by your side.")

30
00:02:12,159 --> 00:02:13,439
(But he didn't.)

31
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:14,680
Maybe.

32
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,240
But you must remember

33
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:19,199
that everything I'm doing

34
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:20,840
is to prepare a gift for you.

35
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:22,919
What gift?

36
00:02:26,199 --> 00:02:27,639
A special gift.

37
00:02:28,319 --> 00:02:30,000
Can't catch it or touch it.

38
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:33,000
But maybe only in the far future

39
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,840
will you understand what it really is.

40
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:39,159
Can't catch it or touch it?

41
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:41,360
Blue sky and white clouds?

42
00:02:44,159 --> 00:02:45,080
Pretty close.

43
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:48,879
So what is it?

44
00:02:48,934 --> 00:02:54,649
♪Life is like a play♪

45
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,439
Just think like this.

46
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,520
Dad's gift

47
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,680
is to stop

48
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,840
Xi's blue sky and white clouds
from disappearing.

49
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:05,800
(Mom always says)

50
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,960
(Dad is a liar.)

51
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:10,120
(But I believe Dad.)

52
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:12,080
(If he promises something,)

53
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,560
(he'll definitely do it.)

54
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,479
Chief Xu.

55
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,560
I think this gift

56
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,439
is worth

57
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:24,960
this trip.

58
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:28,680
In fact, Long is already making

59
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,120
related preparations.

60
00:03:31,039 --> 00:03:32,960
Since you've already made up your mind,

61
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:34,840
okay,

62
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,280
I'll leave it to you.

63
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,520
But remember,

64
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,120
no matter when

65
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,719
or where you are,

66
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,639
never give up hope.

67
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,560
Our organization

68
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:48,319
will certainly do its best

69
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,919
to rescue you.

70
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:52,120
I know.

71
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,800
