74
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:08,719
Will they just let Zheng Taixiang go?

75
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:09,879
Don't worry.

76
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:10,520
It won't happen.

77
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:16,720
There he is.

78
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,519
Murderer!

79
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:22,879
Everyone.

80
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,360
Guys.

81
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,040
Please remain calm.

82
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:29,399
I'm sorry about

83
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:30,720
this old man's passing.

84
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,399
Of course, we also didn't wish

85
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:34,480
for such a tragedy to occur.

86
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,800
But this matter

87
00:04:36,399 --> 00:04:37,319
has nothing to do

88
00:04:37,639 --> 00:04:39,199
with me

89
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,120
or our Tianhai Sect.

90
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,560
It's just that

91
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,720
this old man happened

92
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,720
to suffer a relapse.

93
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,839
If you hadn't gotten physical,
he wouldn't have died!

94
00:04:47,639 --> 00:04:48,600
That's your excuse.

95
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,839
We don't believe it.

96
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,839
No matter what others say,

97
00:04:54,279 --> 00:04:55,399
it doesn't matter.

98
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,240
I want to thank

99
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,879
police officers from Lian'an Town

100
00:04:59,319 --> 00:05:00,759
for proving my innocence.

101
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,160
I really appreciate it.

102
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,199
Everyone.

103
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,319
Please accept my condolences.

104
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,800
Xiu.

105
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,160
Just let him go?

106
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:32,759
Mom.

107
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,360
You're back.

108
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,920
Since you came back,

109
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,920
I've been busy
and haven't had time for you.

110
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,560
I'll make us dinner tonight.

111
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,360
Keep you company.

112
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,639
Mom, I have to leave again.

113
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:51,920
When?

114
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,439
Tomorrow.

115
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,160
So suddenly?

116
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:57,839
I thought

117
00:05:57,839 --> 00:05:59,959
this time you could stay at home
a bit longer.

118
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:03,120
Just started in Taiwan, China.

119
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:04,480
I need to keep an eye.

120
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,879
How long will you be gone?

121
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:06,800
I don't know.

122
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,519
Not sure.

123
00:06:08,319 --> 00:06:09,600
You're doing business,

124
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,199
but I feel you're like in prison.

125
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:12,519
You can't even come home.

126
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,360
This is a special situation.
I have no choice.

127
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,439
Son.

128
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:17,639
What era is it now?

129
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:19,240
Can't tie yourself to one thing.

130
00:06:19,519 --> 00:06:20,000
Listen.

131
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,439
If your business is so tough,

132
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:22,560
then don't do it.

133
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,199
Just come back.

134
00:06:23,199 --> 00:06:24,920
You can just stay at home.

135
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:27,000
I just need to make more food every day.

136
00:06:27,279 --> 00:06:28,560
Three parts of fate

137
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:30,040
and seven parts of hard work.

138
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,199
How can I just easily quit?

139
00:06:33,319 --> 00:06:35,439
If you want to do it, I'll support you.

140
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,240
Keep it up.

141
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,079
Those who strive will win.

142
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,319
Alright.

143
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:45,839
Are you okay by yourself?

144
00:06:46,399 --> 00:06:48,000
Of course, I'm okay.

145
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,360
Why am I not okay?

146
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:50,800
Do you know

147
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,079
that I skipped a few social activities

148
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:55,000
just to make this meal for you?

149
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,199
Come on.

150
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,040
Come on.

151
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,959
I need to tell you something.

152
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,199
What is it?

153
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,319
Do you remember Mr. Wang?

154
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:06,480
Mr. Wang?

155
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,399
When you were little,

156
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:09,279
you wet him all over.

157
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:10,240
What is it? Tell me.

158
00:07:12,319 --> 00:07:13,920
I'm going to marry him.

159
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,560
Which Mr. Wang?

160
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,199
Why are you overreacting?

161
00:07:20,199 --> 00:07:20,759
No.

162
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,360
Which Mr. Wang?

163
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,240
Did you date him? Marriage?

164
00:07:24,519 --> 00:07:25,560
Sit down.

165
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:27,120
Don't worry.

166
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,439
We've known each other for years.

167
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:30,519
Of course, we've dated.

168
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,199
Mr. Wang?

169
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:33,560
I'm telling you,

170
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,600
he might be plain-looking,

171
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:36,879
but

172
00:07:37,199 --> 00:07:38,480
he is very nice.

173
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:40,000
He treats me very well.

174
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,240
He is also very healthy.

175
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,160
I'm telling you...

176
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,519
Alright, healthy.

177
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:46,040
S-Stop it.

178
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:48,160
Anyway,

179
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,519
the situation is just like this.

180
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:53,279
You don't object, do you?

181
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,480
You can't object.

182
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:56,439
Are you happy?

183
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,279
Yes.

184
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:00,639
Of course, I'm happy.

185
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:03,360
This matter

186
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,639
actually doesn't depend on age.

187
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:06,399
Anyway, I feel pretty good.

188
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,079
Good to know.

189
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,920
But you're about to leave.

190
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,120
Seriously.

191
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:16,199
Otherwise, I'll call him over.

192
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:18,279
Let's have a simple ceremony

193
00:08:18,279 --> 00:08:19,680
to make it look a bit formal.

194
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,240
It's fine, you go ahead first.

195
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,360
When the time comes,

196
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,480
let's do a video call.

197
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,759
That works too.

198
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:25,920
My son is understanding.

199
00:08:27,959 --> 00:08:29,360
Let's make it clear first.

200
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:31,279
If you

201
00:08:31,279 --> 00:08:33,039
get a girlfriend,

202
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,720
the kind you want to marry,

203
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:36,440
you have to tell me.

204
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,279
Do you hear me?

205
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,759
You want to check for me?

206
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,759
Of course.

207
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:43,399
What do you know?

208
00:08:44,279 --> 00:08:45,759
At least I have more experience.

209
00:08:47,919 --> 00:08:48,919
Actually,

210
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:50,840
I have a girlfriend.

211
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,440
Why are you so surprised?

212
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,519
You have a girlfriend?

213
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:02,360
