214
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,519
Don't say it yet.

215
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:08,559
I-I'll cook some dishes.

216
00:09:08,639 --> 00:09:09,879
I'll cook some dishes.

217
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:11,200
Pour some wine in a while.

218
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,639
You can tell me then.

219
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,240
Oh my God.

220
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,200
My son has a girlfriend.

221
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:19,480
Oh my God.

222
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,559
