226
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,480
Oh my God.

227
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,799
Don't know if she eats spicy food.

228
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,279
It's not easy now.

229
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:36,279
It's really not easy, son.

230
00:09:55,639 --> 00:09:56,919
What did I say?

231
00:09:58,279 --> 00:09:59,480
I'm sure to beat you.

232
00:10:01,958 --> 00:10:07,456
♪Gather round and drink a few bottles♪

233
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,120
Stop laughing.

234
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,200
You were so timid.

235
00:10:14,879 --> 00:10:16,799
Why did you imitate me and stand up?

236
00:10:19,919 --> 00:10:21,120
Can you learn it?

237
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,679
I'm coming for the last time.

238
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:38,039
I have business and friends now.

239
00:10:38,039 --> 00:10:39,000
I'm very busy.

240
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,159
I don't have time for you.

241
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,039
You are right.

242
00:10:45,799 --> 00:10:47,200
Isn't life always like this?

243
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,320
Learn to enjoy.

244
00:10:54,374 --> 00:10:55,456
♪Come on♪

245
00:10:58,150 --> 00:10:59,040
♪Cheers♪

246
00:11:01,926 --> 00:11:07,463
