♪Don't ponder what may or may not be♪

250
00:11:24,422 --> 00:11:30,786
♪What's in your fate will surely appear♪

251
00:11:31,974 --> 00:11:33,401
♪At this very moment♪

252
00:11:35,462 --> 00:11:37,749
♪We shall wander free and light♪

253
00:11:39,558 --> 00:11:45,905
♪Life is only a few short decades♪

