Taixiang.

258
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:09,960
Don't worry about those people.

259
00:12:10,559 --> 00:12:11,679
The police said

260
00:12:11,679 --> 00:12:12,799
there's no problem with you.

261
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:16,559
I don't care about that old man.

262
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:19,440
