264
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,759
But you're still

265
00:12:27,639 --> 00:12:29,200
in charge of the chemical plant.

266
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,120
It shouldn't be too serious.

267
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:33,919
This is just on the surface.

268
00:12:34,919 --> 00:12:36,039
He has never

269
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,440
