270
00:12:39,759 --> 00:12:40,720
Let me tell you.

271
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,559
He is just testing.

272
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:45,600
He wants to know

273
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,759
what I will do next.

274
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,799
If you want to prove your innocence,

275
00:12:50,399 --> 00:12:51,679
